The paper also discusses the use of empirical findings in research papers, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper involves the use of standardized benchmarks and tuning of baselines, which are topics that fall under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
